    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore asteroids and extract their gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/e67a31cfb21c005cb015fe9490d937ae.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/d03c8fc37eac1722da334ed1593a5ff4.poster.avif?t=1743429631\" width=596 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/d03c8fc37eac1722da334ed1593a5ff4.webm?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/d03c8fc37eac1722da334ed1593a5ff4.mp4?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/e67a31cfb21c005cb015fe9490d937ae.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TIME = DIFFICULTY!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The longer you stay on an asteroid, the faster enemies will spawn, and the more threatening they'll be. You'll need to stay for a while though, because your <span class=\"bb_strike\">evil</span> employer won't let you live if you don't meet your quota! If you really want to excel, try exceeding your quota so you can buy even more upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/aa24be12881cec7ee4cbfb54b1785f45.poster.avif?t=1743429631\" width=596 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/aa24be12881cec7ee4cbfb54b1785f45.webm?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/aa24be12881cec7ee4cbfb54b1785f45.mp4?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/2988722beb81c002fb06f4c6024f8de9.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your gold to buy unique stackable items! Every item is satisfying to use, and quite impactful. Try out combinations of items to find powerful synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/e1fc3f520bd567a01e6fcbae35b22c24.avif?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/2988722beb81c002fb06f4c6024f8de9.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STAT BUFFS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also use your hard-earned gold to improve your stats. These stat buffs aren't typically as strong as items, but they're still important for any asteroid miner. (aka comet rogue)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/999be714742a2ede6324a61144d3cfa2.gif?t=1743429631\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/999be714742a2ede6324a61144d3cfa2.poster.avif?t=1743429631\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/d2b61bf9df90cf50eac598502a58b9af.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FULLY DESTRUCTIBLE PROCEDURALLY-GENERATED ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is procedurally-generated and fully destructible. There are various traps and treasures to be found!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/beda7f45d081e59ca4d19a3c205e01db.poster.avif?t=1743429631\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/beda7f45d081e59ca4d19a3c205e01db.webm?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/beda7f45d081e59ca4d19a3c205e01db.mp4?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/d2b61bf9df90cf50eac598502a58b9af.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCKABLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you die, your gold is automatically put towards unlocking new weapons and pets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/40c377dcb9bbb834ed288b1e112a963e.avif?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=195 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/55a02e66a9167afeea0511be5f9b5061.poster.avif?t=1743429631\" width=200 height=219 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/55a02e66a9167afeea0511be5f9b5061.webm?t=1743429631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/6031849b04292fee029a6b7cbe8640d1.webp?t=1743429631\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLEASE WISHLIST THE GAME, I'M POOR!!! D:</h2>",
